# agentkit

> Agent SDK + runtime + polyglot surface â€” LangChain/LangGraph/CrewAI-class competitor.

Rust core with **Zig/Mojo/Go FFI** + **Python/TypeScript/C# SDKs** + **MCP-native gateway**.

## Workspace layout

```
kits/agentora/
+- Cargo.toml                 workspace root (12 members)
+- agentkit/                  LangChain/LangGraph-class core SDK
+- agentora-graph/            StateGraph runtime (LangGraph-class)
+- agentora-crew/             Multi-agent orchestration (CrewAI/AutoGen-class)
+- agentora-skills/           Skills domain + phenotype-daemon binary
+- agentora-ipc/              UDS+SHM+mpsc IPC primitives
+- agentora-cli/              CLI shell (clap-ext, absorbs helios-cli agent scope)
+- agentora-mcp/              MCP gateway (absorbs MCPForge + agentapi)
+- agentora-obs/              OTel traces + cost metering
+- agentora-py/               PyO3 Python SDK (per-lang repo: KooshaPari/agentkit-py)
+- agentora-ts/               napi-rs TypeScript SDK (per-lang repo: KooshaPari/agentkit-ts)
+- agentora-cs/               C# SDK via csbindgen (per-lang repo: KooshaPari/agentkit-cs)
+- agentora-ffi/              C-ABI + Zig/Mojo FFI core
+- scripts/                   auditor loop, grade.sh, seed-dag.sh, seed_dag.py
+- docs/                      DAG.md, COMPETITIVE.md, BOUNDARY.md, PR_PLAN.md, SDK_REPOS.md
+- .github/workflows/         ci.yml, bench-trend.yml, fuzz-nightly.yml, release.yml
+- .grade-reports/            baseline + per-PR rolling snapshots
+- .dag/                      phenodag + dagctl state (DBs, JSON)
+- .auditors/                 auditor logs + dry-run JSON
```

## Build

```bash
cargo build --workspace --all-features
cargo test  --workspace --all-features
cargo clippy --workspace --all-targets -- -D warnings
cargo fmt   --all -- --check
cargo doc   --workspace --no-deps
```

## Grade

```bash
./scripts/grade.sh . > .grade-reports/baseline-$(date +%Y-%m-%d).json
```

Targets **71+** aggregate per `phenotype-registry/grade.sh` rubric.

## DAG

```bash
./scripts/seed-dag.sh
# then use kits/phenodag CLI to inspect / claim / status
```

Targets **400 nodes** across 8 sub-DAGs (A core, B graph, C crew, D skills+daemon,
E ipc/mcp/obs/ffi, F cli, G py/ts/cs, H hygiene+gov).

## Boundary (out of scope)

`phenotype-infra`, `nanovms`, `phenocompose`, `byteport`, `heliosApp`, `heliosRouter`,
`heliosBench`, `portage`, `heliosLab`.

See `docs/BOUNDARY.md`.

